(1. Introduction) Tj T*
(This is a synthetic GrokRxiv test fixture PDF used by the) Tj T*
(preview-acceptance Playwright spec. It is deliberately small \(so the repo) Tj T*
(stays lean\) but contains enough extractable text to clear the orchestrator's) Tj T*
