() Tj T*
(2. Background) Tj T*
(GrokRxiv runs a typed multi-agent review DAG. The preview) Tj T*
(path extracts text, runs a single Claude pass to produce a structured) Tj T*
(MetaReview, and returns the rendered HTML plus a base64-encoded zip bundle) Tj T*
(of all artifacts. This fixture exercises every step of that pipeline.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(3. Methodology) Tj T*
(The fixture's only methodology is: place enough plain ASCII) Tj T*
(text into a one-page PDF that the pdf-extract Rust crate yields more than) Tj T*
(two hundred characters when invoked on the bytes.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(4. Results) Tj T*
(No results are claimed. This is a smoke fixture, not a paper.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
